flowchart TD
    A[Operator packs + photos parcel] --> B[Book shipment]
    B --> C[Carrier picks up]
    C --> D[Carrier reweighs at hub]
    D --> E{Variance > tolerance?}
    E -->|no| F[No dispute]
    E -->|yes| G[Carrier sends reweigh data]
    G --> H[Auto-eval engine]
    H --> I{Decision}
    I -->|small variance| J[Auto-accept charge]
    I -->|seller evidence strong| K[Auto-dispute via carrier API]
    I -->|needs seller input| L[Open for seller action]
    K --> M[Carrier responds]
    L --> N[Seller adds evidence]
    N --> M
    M --> O{Outcome}
    O -->|seller won| P[Reverse charge in wallet]
    O -->|carrier won| Q[Charge stands]
    O -->|partial| R[Partial reversal]
